## License Structure

This repository uses a dual-license model:

| Scope | Files | License |
| ----- | ----- | ------- |
| Research & Documentation | `Documentacion/`, `protocols/`, `README.md`, all `.md` files outside `src/` | CC BY-NC 4.0 |
| Source Code | `src/`, `analysis/` | GNU AGPL-3.0 |

> Creative Commons explicitly recommends against using CC licenses for software.
> The AGPL-3.0 is used for source code to ensure Open Science compliance
> (OSI-approved) while preventing commercial exploitation.

