## Scope of This License

This license applies to:

- The TCO theoretical framework (Natural Cognitive Frontier, evaluation
  vector model, cognitive tensor architecture, inference model)
- All written documentation, papers, and diagrams in this repository
- The experimental design, hypotheses, and verification protocols
- The MVP architecture specifications and implementation blueprints

This license does NOT restrict:

- Academic citation and reference (with attribution)
- Non-commercial research that builds upon or extends the framework
- Educational use in non-commercial settings

